{
  "stem": "18056.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 181.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we arrived there at-- I think it was in August 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we there till April the 27th, 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To leave?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we-- we worked, of course, there for these months, and we were building that big bunker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Americans came closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British came closer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody got closer, so they started to liquidate those separate camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These camps, by that time, didn't have that much people, that many people, but there were people there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because as time went on, they liquidated also some of the camps, and they would bring the people in into those camps where-- where some life would go on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like my camp got more people in from other camps that were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we just-- one day, they say they going to send us to Tyrol.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we thought, well, that's-- that's another place we got to go to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As they put us on-- on these trains again, and we were driving all night, but we didn't realize that we were going back and forth, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was already kind of closed up, because the Wehrmacht, the-- the-- the-- the army had to have the trains.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they would not give us a chance to go on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So basically, this is how the whole thing happened that we were able to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trains were no different than the ones that they would always carry us, and that was the cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to stand, or if it was not that many people you were able to sit or hang sort of like.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way that you were able to really have a comfort.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no comfortable train, comfortable transportation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just that night, see?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
